Description: `psborrow2` is an R package for complex, innovative trial designs using
   Bayesian dynamic borrowing (BDB). `psborrow2` has two main goals:
   First, `psborrow2` facilitates simulation studies that compare different borrowing
   parameters (e.g. full borrowing, no borrowing, dynamic borrowing) and
   other trial and borrowing characteristics (e.g. sample size, covariates) in
   a unified way; and second, `psborrow2` provides a user-friendly interface for applying BDB
   on the study results handles the MCMC sampling on behalf of the user.
URL: https://github.com/Genentech/psborrow2, https://genentech.github.io/psborrow2/
